data.description: RELAX TO THE SOOTHING SOUNDS OF THE CREEK IN THE NORTH CAROLINA MOUNTAINS!! Nestled in the mountains of North Carolina on a creek, this 2 large bedroom/ 2 bathroom home offers an open floor plan with vaulted ceiling, an office/bonus room, open air side deck, a large screened-in large side deck overlooking the beautiful sounds and view of the creek & mountain, spacious yard...perfect for gardening, PLUS a fenced in area with peach, pear and apple trees. Additionally there is a mulberry tree and blue berry bushes.
